ubuntu-docviewer-app (2.0) vivid; urgency=medium

  * Updated application icon (LP: #1476659 and LP: #1432392)
  * Updated translations
  * Added support to Office documents through libreofficekit
  * General performance improvements
  * UX more consistent with the design guidelines
  * Updated to ubuntu-sdk-14.04.1 (QtQuick 2.4 and Ubuntu.Components 1.3) (LP: #1508363)
  * A more intuitive UI when importing a new document
  * Added a 'share' action for exporting a document to another app/web service (LP: #1494818)
  * Removed GridView from documents page (will be reintroduced in future)
  * Refactored app initialization
  * Better zoom support on desktop
  * Switched to QML Ubuntu.ContentHub APIs (LP: #1469422)
  * Switched to QML Ubuntu.Components.Arguments APIs
  * Changed header behaviour in the PDF viewer (LP: #1453403)

 -- Stefano Verzegnassi <verzegnassi.stefano@gmail.com>  Sat, 28 Nov 2015 13:30:55 +0100

